vikramaditya ( english : phantom ) is a 2014 indian action thriller film directed by vikramaditya motwane and produced by &lt;unk&gt; motwane under the banner of phantom films . the film is directed by vikramaditya motwane . the film is based on the novel of the same name by vikramaditya motwane . the film is scheduled to be released in 2017 .